prompts.frontCover: Dynamic comic book style greeting card front cover. A vibrant beach scene is depicted using bold colors, thick black outlines, and halftone dot patterns for shading. A super-heroine, who is the main focus, stands triumphantly in a classic comic book power pose on the sand, one hand on her hip, the other holding a giant, delicious-looking boba tea like a trophy. She has a joyful and confident expression. The sky is a brilliant, pop-art-style sunset with dramatic yellow and orange sunburst rays. In the background, stylized ocean waves crash onto the shore. The entire scene has a sense of action and fun. In the center of the image, written in a beautiful, readable, and slightly stylized handwritten cursive script, is the text "Happy Birthday to my Super-Lao Lao!". The text is integrated into the scene, perhaps within a classic comic book caption box or speech bubble with a dynamic outline. The overall composition is energetic, fun, and visually striking, capturing a playful and celebratory mood. Flat 2D artwork.
